<DIV style="font-family: 'Times New Roman',Times,serif">



<DIV align="left" style="font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 6pt">asset securitization programs. The cost of funding Cardmember receivables and loans is a
major expense of Card operations. (You can find a discussion of TRS&#146; and Centurion Bank&#146;s
securitization and other financing activities on page&nbsp;32,
