    <TD width="3%" nowrap align="left"><B>&#149;</B></TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD>Corporate Card, issued to individuals through a corporate account
established by their employer and designed primarily for travel and entertainment
spending;</TD>
