Public Accountants &#150; Audit Fees;&#148; &#147; &#150; Audit-Related Fees;&#148; &#147; &#150; Tax Fees;&#148; &#147; &#150; All Other Fees;&#148; and &#147; &#150; Policy on Pre-Approval of Services Provided by
Independent Registered Public Accountants,&#148; which will appear in the Company&#146;s definitive proxy
statement in connection with our Annual Meeting of Shareholders to be held April&nbsp;23, 2007, is
incorporated herein by reference.
